<br>
When you zone very low on health, the game engine puts you at a safe spot--it should also wipe all your buffs. I've done this a couple of times leaving OS--zone out with 150 or so hp, wind up buffless next to EJ zone. #<br>
<br>
If my buffs had been stripped, I'd have written it off as the &quot;died while zoning&quot; feature.  But in fact all of my buffs were still intact...<br>
<br>
I ended up standing between those two wimpy lizards that stand just inside the first set of double-doors (&quot;inside&quot; meaning &quot;in the zone tunnel&quot;, and not on the side out in the courtyard).<br>
